# Merge Sort Visualization

## Merge Sort Tree Diagram

- Start with the array: `[38, 27, 43, 3, 9, 82, 10]`

### Divide Phase:
1. `[38, 27, 43, 3, 9, 82, 10]`
  -  /   \
2. `[38, 27, 43]`   `[3, 9, 82, 10]`
  -  /      \ 
3. `[38, 27]`   `[43]`   `[3, 9]`   `[82, 10]`
  -  /   \         -  /   \ 
4. `[38]`  `[27]`   `[43]`   `[3]`  `[9]`   `[82]`  `[10]`

### Merge Phase:
1. Merging `[38]`  and  `[27]` -> `[27, 38]`

2. Merging `[27, 38]` and `[43]` -> `[27, 38, 43]`

3. Merging `[3]` and `[9]` -> `[3, 9]`

4. Merging `[82]` and `[10]` -> `[10, 82]`

5. Merging `[3, 9]` and `[10, 82]` -> `[3, 9, 10, 82]`

6. Finally, merging `[27, 38, 43]` and `[3, 9, 10, 82]` -> `[3, 9, 10, 27, 38, 43, 82]`

## Result:
- Sorted Array: `[3, 9, 10, 27, 38, 43, 82]`